ney already present, the safest next move is a light body-first check-in rather than backlog review, symbolic interpretation, or a more intense practice invitation.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"readActions\\\\\\\":[\\\\\\\"alive_today read of recent re-entry signals\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"alive_today read of active journey context\\\\\\\"],\\\\\\\"selectedMoveKind\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ask_body_checkin\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"selectedSurface\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"alive_today\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"selectedToolSequence\\\\\\\":[\\\\\\\"circulatio_alive_today\\\\\\\"],\\\\\\\"toolArgsSummary\\\\\\\":{},\\\\\\\"turnId\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"t1\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"writeActions\\\\\\\":[]}]}\\\"}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"turn.completed\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input_tokens\\\":29709,\\\"cached_input_tokens\\\":2432,\\\"output_tokens\\\":2824}}\\n\",\n  \"warnings\": [\n    \"Unrecognized tool alias 'alive_today read of recent re-entry signals'.\",\n    \"Unrecognized tool alias 'alive_today read of active journey context'.\"\n  ]\n}\n```"}],"structured_content":null},"error":null,"status":"completed"}}
